(1, '20181001102228748.jpg', 'Fitness/Sport', 'fitness-sport', 'Fitness/Sport: Gym Tiles', 'Home and Commerical Gym Flooring | Recylced Rubber Flooring', 'We manufacture gym tiles from recycled rubber for commerical gym flooring and home use. Design your projects with Dinoflex rubber flooring', '20181023121854429.svg', 'Fitness/Sport: Gym Tiles', 'Looking for new flooring or exercise mats for your home gym or commercial facility? Our rubber gym flooring is the &lsquo;perfect surface&rsquo; for any commercial or residential workout area &ndash; big or small.&nbsp; We offer an extensive product line for gym flooring.', '20181017114357627.jpg', 3, 1, '2018-10-01 10:22:28', '2021-02-25 09:19:22'),
(2, '20181002065437757.jpg', 'Ice Arena', 'ice-arena', 'Ice Arena', 'Ice Arena', 'Our ice arena flooring products are super durable, attractive, and made right here in North America. Dinoflex has been providing premium rubber flooring solutions for recreational applications for decades.', '20181204205359299.svg', 'Headline', 'Tough on wear, and easy on skate blades, Dinoflex flooring stands up against sharp skates without chipping or dulling blades. Versatile enough to use throughout a facility this easy to clean surface holds up under high traffic and rough use.', '20181017114425848.jpg', 6, 1, '2018-10-02 06:54:37', '2019-05-14 08:14:19'),
(3, '20181002065532714.jpg', 'Ski Resort', 'ski-resort', 'Ski Resort', 'Ski Resort', 'Wet and slippery floors are a major concern for any business; ski resorts have to deal with more water inside their business than in almost any other industry. Rubber flooring makes a great safety addition to any ski resort.', '20181204204802963.svg', 'Headline', 'Get a grip with our rugged and durable rubber flooring. Slip-resistant rubber is impervious to snow, ice, moisture, gravel and dirt making it ideal for mountain resorts and recreation facilities catering to outdoor enthusiasts. Enjoy an easy to clean surface that holds up under high traffic and rough use.', '20181017114445288.jpg', 8, 1, '2018-10-02 06:55:32', '2019-05-14 11:33:44'),
(4, '20181002070021211.jpg', 'Commercial/Retail', 'commercial-retail', 'Commercial/Retail', 'Commercial/Retail', 'Dinoflex commercial flooring is hard-wearing, sustainable recycled rubber tile. It’s simply the most practical flooring for your business. Our flooring is striking in design, low in maintenance & high in durability.', '20181017111942616.svg', 'Headline', 'Dinoflex commercial flooring is a hard-wearing alternative flooring solution for today&rsquo;s building design. Enjoy a variety of choices from custom to curated colors in a durable and low maintenance flooring systems.', '20181017114521455.jpg', 1, 1, '2018-10-02 07:00:21', '2019-05-13 12:04:32'),
(5, '20181002070110227.jpg', 'Hospitality', 'hospitality', 'Hospitality', 'Hospitality', 'Choosing the right flooring for restaurant dining areas is both an art and a science. Whether the dining room areas are in the quick service, casual, family or fine dining, we have a solution for you.', '20181023064628993.svg', 'Headline', 'Choosing the right commercial flooring is both an art and a science. From restaurant dining and bar service to gift shops, corridors, and staff areas we have a range of flooring designed to cover every service area.', '20200813062636979.jpg', 5, 1, '2018-10-02 07:01:10', '2020-08-13 06:26:36'),
(6, '20181002070150886.jpg', 'Education', 'education', 'Education', 'Education', 'Education spaces at all levels are now designed to serve multiple purposes, school flooring must demonstrate flexibility. School floors contribute greatly to the health, safety and comfort of students and teachers.', '20181017112018400.svg', 'Headline', 'Education facilities at every level contribute to the health, safety, and comfort of students, teachers, and staff. Specially designed to serve a variety of purposes, education centers require environmentally conscious flooring designed to provide solutions for every space.', '20181017114650715.jpg', 2, 1, '2018-10-02 07:01:50', '2020-07-14 20:22:21'),
(7, '20191001173747450.jpg', 'Health Care', 'health-care', 'Health Care', 'Health Care', 'Our rubber flooring options have indentation resistance and low maintenance durable finishes; let us inspire your great healthcare space with our flooring solutions. We can meet the demands of the clinical environment.', '20181017112036354.svg', 'Headline', 'Our rubber flooring options have indentation resistance and low maintenance durable finishes.  Let us inspire your healthcare spaces with our flooring solutions that meet the demands of your busy clinical enviornments.', '20181017114728177.jpg', 4, 1, '2018-10-02 07:02:34', '2020-07-13 21:18:52'),
(8, '20181002070315241.jpg', 'Other', 'other', 'Other', 'Other', 'Dinoflex has provides a diverse collection of solutions to our clients for their recycled rubber needs. Our process produces an impressive range of richly colored flooring suitable for a multitude of applications.', '20181017112103176.svg', 'Headline', 'Dinoflex provides a diverse collection of solutions to our clients for their recycled rubber needs. Our process produces an impressive range of richly colored flooring suitable for a multitude of applications.', '20181017114748933.jpg', 9, 1, '2018-10-02 07:03:15', '2019-07-11 05:11:41'),
(9, '20181002070354159.jpg', 'Location', 'location', 'Location', 'Location', 'Location', NULL, 'Headline', 'Headline', '20181002070354423.jpg', 7, 0, '2018-10-02 07:03:54', '2018-12-03 10:15:47');
