(4, '202102032139329.jpg', 'Gym matting options for commercial and home gyms', 'Gym Matting Options for Commercial and Home Gyms', 'Recycled rubber gym flooring is an essential part of any gym or sporting facility design. Discover the benefits of these durable flooring products. ', 'gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms', '<p>Recycled rubber flooring is the preferred choice when it comes to <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/sport-mat-flooring\" title=\"Sport Mat Flooring\">flooring for gyms</a> and fitness centers. The traction and shock absorbing qualities of recycled rubber flooring make it the perfect material to support the running, jumping, falling and weight-dropping that are routine parts of a workout. Rubber has natural anti-fatigue capabilities, as it cushions any weight placed on it. It is also extremely versatile, coming in a wide range of hardnesses to suit your fitness facility’s specific needs. If you are looking for the perfect flooring solution for your fitness facility, this guide to the many options and considerations will help you make the right choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"blog pic-1\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/PillarPhoto1.jpg\"></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/fitness-equipment-flooring-for-gyms\"><strong>Fitness equipment recycled rubber flooring for gyms</strong></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you are outfitting a major commercial fitness center or a small home gym, recycled rubber<a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/sport-mat-flooring\"> fitness flooring</a> is a necessity. A gym floor needs to be able to protect against impact and fatigue, as well as prevent slipping. Gym equipment is heavy and can easily damage most flooring made of other materials, such as wood or ceramic tile. In turn, hard floors can damage equipment and result in athlete injuries. A good<a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/best-use/fitness-sport\"> recycled rubber flooring</a> product provides the padding and impact absorption qualities needed to protect floors, equipment and gym users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/give-your-clients-the-best-gym-rubber-flooring\"><strong>More people are working out at home: give your clients the best gym flooring</strong></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The COVID-19 lockdowns of the past year have led to many gyms having to close, either temporarily or permanently. As a result, many housebound fitness fanatics have brought their workouts into the home. Where possible, many people are equipping complete in-home gyms. These personal home fitness facilities need proper recycled rubber flooring to protect floors and equipment. Even if people are engaging in exercise that is centred on callisthenics, yoga or aerobics, they still need rubber flooring that can protect against impact and recycled rubber flooring matting is that solution! If you have been contracted to design and build a home gym, incorporating recycled rubber flooring is a critical part of your installation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/PillarPhoto2.png\"></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/recycled-rubber-sports-flooring\"><strong>Recycled rubber sports flooring</strong></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Recycled rubber matting is essential, not only for gyms, but for any sports facility. Fitness clubs, sports clubs, ice arenas, ski hills and other venues require tough but flexible flooring with a high degree of traction and shock absorption. Dinoflex’s <a href=\"http://dinoflex.com/best-use/fitness-sport\">Sport Mat fitness flooring</a> is the perfect flooring solution for these needs. Versatile in its application, Sport Mat will support health and recreation activities at every level. Be it weights, fitness machines, skate blades, ski boots, golf clubs or more, Sport Mat will provide the absorptive powers you need to protect both your floors and users. Manufactured from recycled rubber, Sport Mat provides a safer workout environment by reducing the risk of falls, allows for healthy air intake with its low VOC, and is guaranteed never to curl. The best part is, with Sport Mat you can have your recycled rubber tiles displayed with your logo for branding that will never fade or show wear patterns.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/Recycle-rubber-flooring-for-commercial-spaces\"><strong>Rubber flooring for commercial spaces</strong></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Recycled rubber matting is not only for sports and fitness facilities. You can use it in commercial spaces too. Design in these areas involves a balance of aesthetics and function, and <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/best-use/commercial-retail\">Dinoflex’s Evolution Commercial Flooring</a> offers you both. Designers have used all sorts of flooring materials for commercial spaces: wood, tile, carpet, and more. As its name suggests, our Evolution product is the natural development of all the strengths and challenges of these materials. Offering high traction, underfoot comfort, sound reduction capabilities, stain resistance, easy cleaning, extreme durability and vibrant colours, Evolution Commercial Flooring is perfect for a variety of commercial designs and flooring applications. Made from recycled rubber tires and EPDM, by incorporating this product into your commercial space design, you will provide your clients a quieter, cleaner, and safer space for their work, all while earning green credits, too.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/top-6-uses-of-rubber-mat-flooring\"><strong>Top 6 uses of recycled rubber </strong><strong>mat</strong><strong> flooring</strong></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As is probably quite clear already, recycled rubber flooring is a wonderfully versatile flooring option that works exceptionally well in a variety of environments. Here are six of the most common uses to which recycled rubber flooring is the ideal flooring option:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Gyms: </strong>Recycled rubber flooring provides tough, shock absorbing attributes needed to protect floors, equipment and people in high-impact environments, characteristic of home gyms and fitness centers.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Commercial spaces: </strong>Heavy foot traffic and stringent cleaning requirements dictate what kind of flooring can be used in commercial spaces. In addition to the durability required to cater for these needs, commercial flooring must also meet a high aesthetic standard and a variety of design needs. Recycled rubber flooring offers all of those, and more.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Sporting venues: </strong>From ice arenas to ski hills and more, every sporting venue can benefit from recycled rubber flooring. Offering high traction and impact absorption with excellent performance in wet and dry conditions makes recycled rubber flooring ideal to support athletic activities of all kinds.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Decks and walkways: </strong>Both decorative and durable, recycled rubber mat surfacing is an excellent flooring choice option for outdoor locations such as decks, walkways and even roofs. They are an all-weather solution that can be worked into your designs for landscapes, gardens and outside entertainment areas.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Children’s play areas: </strong><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/playground-tiles\">Rubber play tiles</a> are water permeable and slip resistant, providing a comfortable, durable surface on which children can play safely. Their excellent shock absorbing qualities make them ideal for keeping children safe if they fall from a higher height.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Barns and animal enclosures: </strong>Flooring mats made from recycled, non-vulcanized rubber are tough, odorless and safe for indoor and outdoor use in animal enclosures. The dense rubber is easy to clean, provides a non-slip surface for livestock to walk on and facilitates a hygienic environment for animals and the people who care for them.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/dinoflex-recycled-rubber-flooring-for-gyms\"><strong>Customer favourite gym mats</strong></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Most people looking for recycled rubber flooring have three attributes in mind: aesthetics, durability and sustainability. Among those who opt for Dinoflex’s flooring solutions, most are designing either commercial spaces or sports and fitness facilities. Evolution <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/best-use/commercial-retail\">Commercial Flooring</a> is extremely popular among those in the former category, as this product brings together design and durability in a recycled rubber flooring mat that can carry the weight of heavy foot traffic, is easy to clean and comes in a range of colours and patterns to suit any visual requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to fitness and sporting facilities, our Sport Mat is the most popular choice. Incredibly versatile, this recycled rubber flooring mat serves just as effectively in a home gym as in a major sporting facility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being made of recycled rubber, all of our products have a high degree of sustainability and as mentioned previously, Nature’s Collection is a favourite among customers who place a particular emphasis on this criterion. Sustainably harvested cork is blended in with recycled rubber to create an even more environmentally friendly flooring, while also checking the boxes for underfoot comfort, durability and sound absorption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/PillarPhoto3.png\"></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/benefits-of-recycled-rubber-floor-tiles\"><strong>Pros of designing with recycled rubber flooring </strong></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Why include recycled rubber matting in your flooring designs? The functional and aesthetic benefits should be apparent from the discussion thus far. Let’s take a closer look at the benefits of recycled rubber floor tiles:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Resilience: </strong>Recycled rubber floors can carry enormous amounts of regular foot traffic, even in high impact conditions. They are also water resistant, and thus impervious to spills and stains, which can easily be washed off. What makes them especially suitable for gyms is that they provide more cushioning than other flooring types, which improves comfort and reduces injuries and fatigue.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Slip resistance: </strong>Gyms and similar facilities are places in which injuries are of a relatively high risk. Flooring shouldn’t add to these risks. Recycled rubber floors reduce the risk of slipping, keeping users safe and focused on their training.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Aesthetic versatility: </strong>Recycled rubber floors mats and tiles can offer a wide range of options to suit your stylistic requirements. With unlimited colors and a range of patterning options to complete and accent your designs, recycled rubber flooring is the ideal flooring choice for so many venues and facilities.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p><strong>Sustainability: </strong>With so many different recycled rubber flooring products exhibited in the Dinoflex name, you can rest assured that you have selected a solution that not only fulfils your stylistic and functional requirements, but also reduces the carbon footprint of your facility.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/home\">Dinoflex</a> is a trusted flooring brand that has developed a formidable reputation for quality and sustainability through our constant dedication to constant innovation. Our products inspire and assist architects and designers to create spaces that exceed expectations in terms of form and function. <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/contact\">Contact us</a> to find out more about how our recycled rubber matting innovations can enhance your commercial or home gym design. In addition to all the reasons mentioned above, all of our recycled rubber flooring tiles are also guaranteed never to curl!</p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-02-02', 1, '2018-10-03 13:48:31', '2021-02-19 11:23:02'),
(7, '2021042706150586.jpg', 'Fitness equipment flooring for gyms', 'Fitness equipment flooring for gyms', 'Recycled rubber flooring is an indispensable part of any gym. Learn about the main qualities that make rubber flooring so important.', 'fitness-equipment-flooring-for-gyms', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">When building and equipping a new gym, whether it’s a major commercial health club or a dedicated exercise space within a client’s home, flooring for your fitness equipment and fitness areas are an indispensable part of your design. Whether a fitness center is big or small, incorporating </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/indoor-products\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">recycled rubber flooring</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> in your gym design is essential due to these main recycled rubber flooring attributes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\"><img alt=\"Fitness equipment flooring for gyms\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/Fitness equipment flooring for gyms.png\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad3bff27-7fff-7ba6-f9ff-bf290cc2aa87\"><span xss=\"removed\">1. Protection</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2859f8e6-7fff-eab5-9e48-6c3ff66ffa31\"><span xss=\"removed\">Gym equipment is heavy and usually features hard angles and corners that can damage wooden and tiled floors. Your fitness flooring needs to protect surfaces from the weight and impact of gym machines. In turn, hard floors can even cause damage to the equipment. A good recycled  rubber flooring product provides the padding and impact absorption qualities needed to protect floors, equipment and gym users. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-dac78f0f-7fff-ac2c-dbdd-4bc62b765db4\"><span xss=\"removed\">2. Shock absorption and Traction</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-bfd0c91c-7fff-e397-4164-0bfc604c466c\"><span xss=\"removed\">Hard floors - whether made of wood, ceramic tile or vinyl, hard floors do not provide traction which makes slipping a severe risk. The use of gym machines causes vibrations that possibly cause machines to shift and become unstable, potentially damaging floors, injuring users, as well as making a gym unnecessarily noisy. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/best-use/fitness-sport\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">rubber flooring</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> provides traction by absorbing shock and vibration, thus preventing these potential problems. These shock absorbing qualities also make working out more comfortable for gym users, particularly when they step off the machines to do aerobic or calisthenic exercises.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-71909c42-7fff-0430-ca8a-b330c2ec49ef\"><span xss=\"removed\">Where do you go to find the fitness facility flooring needed for your next health club or home gym project? </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/#loaded\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Contact Dinoflex</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> to find the ideal solution. Our line of recycled rubber flooring is guaranteed never to curl, moisture resistant, and is highly durable. With little to no VOC, Dinoflex recycled rubber floors allow for healthy air intake and our rubber flooring will not deteriorate over time. </span></span><br>\r\n </p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-01-04', 1, '2021-02-18 15:41:05', '2021-04-27 06:15:05'),
(8, '20210219083728419.png', 'Give your home gym clients the best gym rubber flooring', 'Give your home gym clients the best gym flooring', 'When designing a home gym, you need to factor gym flooring into your plans. Find out why this is important and what your options are.', 'give-your-clients-the-best-gym-rubber-flooring', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-88e24ed7-7fff-cfce-6197-76b53f2adeee\"><span xss=\"removed\">The COVID-19 lockdowns of the past year have led to many gyms having to close, either temporarily or permanently. As a result, many fitness fanatics have been housebound and have had to find alternative ways to keep themselves in shape.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\"><img alt=\"Give your home gym clients the best gym rubber flooring \" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/Give your home gym clients the best gym rubber flooring.png\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5ff6476f-7fff-f83c-2b26-258ec34a7f4d\"><span xss=\"removed\">Why home gyms need recycled rubber flooring</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1ee511e-7fff-219f-35a8-c276ade503dc\"><span xss=\"removed\">Where possible, many people are equipping complete in-home gyms. As much as these personal </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/specialty-products\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">home fitness facilities</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> need quality machines and other fitness equipment, they also need gym flooring to protect the users, the flooring underneath, and the equipment itself. Even if people are engaging in exercise that is centred on callisthenics, yoga or aerobics rather than weights or machines, they still need recycled rubber flooring that can protect against impact and reduce the risk of falls. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">If you have been contracted to design and build a </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/specialty-products\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">home gym</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> for a client, incorporating recycled rubber flooring is a critical part of your installation because of its shock and sound absorbing properties. As they focus on their fitness, your clients will enjoy the thermal benefits and comfort under their feet from our recycled rubber flooring! </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3a5d432b-7fff-5088-64cf-0f81b3058481\"><span xss=\"removed\">Home gym flooring options</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-46ecf75d-7fff-7fde-b404-256ec0d3a3b3\"><span xss=\"removed\">Dinoflex has several product offerings that will be ideal for your clients’ home gyms. Consider the following options:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8f2536d0-7fff-ae9c-5efb-11c97a749488\"><strong><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/sport-mat-flooring\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Sport mat</span></a><span xss=\"removed\">: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Our entry-level mat is designed with the fitness fanatic in mind, offering shock absorption and traction to keep the athlete working out at their peak performance.</span></span></li>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-7d6c0647-7fff-e3bc-2f38-2e88d1034678\"><strong><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/vulca-no-sport\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Vulca-No Sport</span></a><span xss=\"removed\">: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">A versatile flooring solution that works just as well for ice rinks or sports arenas, as for home gyms.</span></span></li>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-925b7c4e-7fff-6892-d777-87e38c8df59a\"><strong><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/evolution-commercial\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Evolution Flooring</span></a><span xss=\"removed\">:</span><span xss=\"removed\"> </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">High traction, underfoot comfort and superior sound reducing properties are the favorites amongst this product, making it an ideal option for a home gym floor.</span></span></li>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0fed0fda-7fff-3893-6fea-2e47f12c6e0d\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/high-impact\" xss=\"removed\">Next Step High Impact</a>:</span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">The ultimate in traction, shock absorption and soundproofing for prolonged training endurance.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-fa1ed7c9-7fff-9fa7-ccff-ae96ef04d045\"><span xss=\"removed\">Contact Dinoflex to find out which </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/specialty-products\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">gym flooring</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> solution is right for your next home gym project.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-01-11', 1, '2021-02-19 08:37:28', '2021-02-19 11:02:27'),
(9, '20210219091739862.png', 'Sustainable gym flooring made for designers', 'Sustainable gym flooring made for designers', 'Recycled rubber gym flooring can be tough, durable and attractively designed, while also being sustainably manufactured. Learn more here.', 'sustainable-gym-flooring-made-for-designers', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-bd57ec91-7fff-87b6-10dc-ccb2313e4f9e\"><span xss=\"removed\">A common objection to recycled rubber gym floors is that they are not environmentally friendly. At Dinoflex, we know offering unique solutions means doing things differently. Rubber is a highly sustainable and easily </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">recyclable material</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> that can be reused to manufacture high-quality flooring materials. Dinoflex is committed to producing recycled rubber flooring that is as sustainable in its production as it is effective in its application.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\"><img alt=\"Sustainable gym flooring made for designers\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/Sustainable gym flooring made for designers.png\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-f0688cde-7fff-a802-aaf7-91ae16295e20\"><span xss=\"removed\">Environmentally friendly gym flooring options</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-924ce3b8-7fff-d87e-07fd-933644cde741\"><span xss=\"removed\">Consider two of Dinoflex’s flooring solutions as excellent examples of how rubber flooring can be both sustainable and effective.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2f2011c1-7fff-fdab-5faf-5de7cc4d5dc7\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/high-impact\" xss=\"removed\">Next Step-High Impact</a></span><span xss=\"removed\"> - </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">prolonged training is easy and risk free on this flooring surface. The highly durable backing provides the support athletes need, allowing them to focus on nothing else but their fitness. </span></span></li>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ffb69165-7fff-3bcc-6d32-6cd26eed327e\"><strong><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/vulca-no-sport\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Vulca-NO!</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> - </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">This unique, high-density matting is produced by way of a special process that does not involve vulcanization, making it completely free of harmful solvents and volatile organic compounds, resulting in a tough and odorless rubber flooring option.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a4f17ce0-7fff-c57c-4a00-6f4891c22806\"><span xss=\"removed\">Sustainability and function - without sacrificing aesthetics</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-86ac9fa3-7fff-f1c2-71bf-0545d2025969\"><span xss=\"removed\">While some of our eco-friendly gym flooring options are created with function and durability as their main attributes, most of our products are available with a variety of colours, textures and application methods to suit all design demands. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">Our </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/high-impact-extreme\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Next Step-Extreme</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> flooring offers radical sound absorption properties while minimizing disturbance to others. But, with an unlimited color selection, the aesthetics of a facility can match the high level of resiliency needed.  Our </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/color-innovator/\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Color Innovator</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> allows you to create a custom color  for your desired applications without compromising performance.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c27ad174-7fff-1725-747c-720340b2a7ad\"><span xss=\"removed\">For more information on Dinoflex’s sustainable recycled rubber gym flooring options, </span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/contact\" xss=\"removed\">contact us</a>.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-01-20', 1, '2021-02-19 08:48:57', '2021-02-19 09:17:39'),
(10, '20210219091018172.png', 'Recycled rubber sports flooring', 'Recycled rubber sports flooring', 'Sports flooring is essential when building a fitness facility. Learn about a recycled rubber matting solution that is perfect for your next gym design project.', 'recycled-rubber-sports-flooring', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-bfded8bf-7fff-162f-8c02-1a5b7a113c21\"><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber sports flooring is essential, not only for gyms, but for any sports facility. A variety of sports clubs such as climbing gyms, ski resorts, ice arenas and other venues require tough, flexible flooring with a high degree of traction and shock absorption. Dinoflex is dedicated to creating quality versatile recycled rubber </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/best-use/fitness-sport\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">flooring</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> options for all kinds of facilities, from home gyms to multi-purpose sports facilities.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\"><img alt=\"Recycled rubber sports flooring\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/Recycled rubber sports flooring.png\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8f59c7c8-7fff-33c0-94b8-f6642892a830\"><span xss=\"removed\">Multi-purpose rubber flooring</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-9d7bfbc9-7fff-654f-f436-5b77d89a94e2\"><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/sport-mat-flooring\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Sport Mat</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> is Dinoflex’s entry level </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/best-use/fitness-sport\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">sports flooring</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> solution, designed with athletes in mind. It is a versatile rubber flooring product that will support health and recreation activities at every level. From machines to free weights, our Sport Mat will provide the absorptive power needed from the weight and impact exerted on your flooring. Manufactured from recycled rubber, Sport Mat makes for a safer work environment by reducing the risk of falls, handling weight and impact, and allows for healthy air intake due to low VOC in the manufacturing process. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">Moisture resistant, Dinoflex’s recycled rubber flooring products will not deteriorate over time and will contribute to your facility’s green rating. You can also have the rubber tiles printed with </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/custom-floor-design-and-logos\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">your logo for branding</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> that will never fade. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-88fb798d-7fff-9706-d283-134f1bf74084\"><span xss=\"removed\">Like all our products, Sport Mat will not show wear patterns and is guaranteed never to curl. The beauty of this product is while it is perfect for large, commercial gyms or high-capacity sports arenas, it is also ideal for home gyms of any size. Home gyms have grown in popularity over the past year as people have been confined to their homes and gyms have had to close, either temporarily or permanently.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-67e07cdb-7fff-b3ee-df84-1b0aab314e30\"><span xss=\"removed\">When you are called upon to design and construct a home gym, make Dinoflex Sport Mat your first sports flooring choice. </span><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/contact\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Contact us</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> for more information about Sport Flooring and our other recycled rubber flooring solutions.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-01-25', 1, '2021-02-19 09:10:18', '2021-02-19 09:14:10'),
(11, '20210219092527552.png', 'Recycle rubber flooring for commercial spaces', 'Recycled rubber flooring for commercial spaces', 'If you are seeking the right rubber flooring for a new commercial space project, find out why Dinoflex’s unique solution is exactly what you need.', 'Recycle-rubber-flooring-for-commercial-spaces', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-fbfa1cbf-7fff-9c97-99b1-85857414d6a8\"><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber flooring is a versatile material known for both its aesthetic and functional properties. This is why it is used in a variety of establishments that span from retail spaces to fitness facilities. Each space requires its flooring to have specific design and manufacture capabilities to suit its purpose most effectively. There are similarities in function between recycled <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">rubber flooring</a> types, but depending on their purpose, optimizations among products exist. These differences have enabled us to offer nine different types of indoor recycled rubber flooring options to complement different flooring needs.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\"><img alt=\"Recycle rubber flooring for commercial spaces\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/Recycle rubber flooring for commercial spaces.png\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c331f4e4-7fff-d797-d677-f13d92bb07b9\"><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber flooring that balances aesthetics and function  </span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-f4831da4-7fff-012c-7e99-f4c07561cd00\"><span xss=\"removed\">Design for flooring intended for commercial spaces involves a balance of aesthetics and function. At Dinoflex, we developed Evolution Commercial Flooring as a response to a flooring product that offers you both. Designers have incorporated all sorts of flooring materials for commercial spaces ranging from wood to tile to carpet, and more.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">As its name suggests, this flooring product is the natural evolution and progression from those commonly used materials to recycled rubber flooring. Offering high traction, underfoot comfort, sound reduction capabilities, stain resistance, easy cleaning, extreme durability and vibrant colours are just some of the features one will find in Evolution Commercial Flooring. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-147b0d35-7fff-40b6-d6e4-536f799d8222\"><span xss=\"removed\">If you’re a commercial space designer, using our Evolution recycled <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">rubber flooring</a> in your commercial space design will help you create a quieter, cleaner and safer space while also earning LEED credits for your clients. With no minimum size orders and 70-plus standard colours to choose from means here at Dinoflex, we can create a colour blend that is unique to your desired look. Being FloorScore® certified for air quality, you can rest assured your flooring choice is ticking all the boxes for your clients.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-65a75a8c-7fff-6123-0e4f-d4713f67b105\"><span xss=\"removed\">Evolution Commercial Flooring is the ideal recycled rubber flooring option for any commercial space that needs a hardwearing, high function and sustainable surface. Contact us at Dinoflex for more information on our <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">recycled rubber flooring</a> solutions.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-02-03', 1, '2021-02-19 09:25:27', '2021-02-24 14:43:26'),
(12, '20210427061418613.jpg', 'Top 6 uses of rubber mat flooring', 'Top 6 uses of recycled rubber mat flooring', 'Recycled rubber mat flooring is extremely versatile. Find out about six of its most common uses and the best solutions for each purpose.', 'top-6-uses-of-rubber-mat-flooring', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber is a versatile flooring option that works exceptionally well in a variety of environments. Here are six of the most common applications for recycled rubber flooring, complemented with our most suitable recycled rubber flooring options.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\"><img alt=\"Top 6 uses of rubber mat flooring\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/Top 6 uses of rubber mat flooring.png\" xss=\"removed\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-fc474387-7fff-8c61-0bd3-5d914b6d8472\"><span xss=\"removed\">The best recycled rubber flooring mats for every purpose</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-d9e9ea88-7fff-d08e-1ba3-aa664f32f3ab\"><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber flooring is used in all kinds of spaces of different sizes, both indoor and outdoor. Read on below for the most common applications of recycled rubber flooring. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8812fab1-7fff-15bf-202c-d1727b33f8e2\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Gyms: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber flooring provides the tough, shock-absorbing layer needed to protect floors, equipment and people in high-impact environments characteristic of <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">home gyms</a> and fitness centers. At Dinoflex, we offer several flooring solutions for gyms of all sizes, including our Sport Mat, Vulca-NO!, Stride Fitness Tiles and Next Step High Impact. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8812fab1-7fff-15bf-202c-d1727b33f8e2\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Commercial spaces: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Heavy foot traffic and stringent cleaning requirements dictate what kinds of flooring can be used in commercial spaces. In addition to the durability required to cater for these needs, <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">commercial flooring</a> must also meet a high aesthetic standard and a variety of design needs. It’s a tall order for which recycled rubber flooring offers all that is needed, and more. Our Evolution Commercial Flooring has been developed with commercial spaces in mind.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8812fab1-7fff-15bf-202c-d1727b33f8e2\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Sporting venues: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Be it ski resorts or ice rinks, every sporting venue can make use of recycled rubber flooring. Ideal for high traction areas where shock absorption is needed but also exhibiting excellent performance in wet and dry conditions, makes <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">recycled rubber flooring</a> the ideal choice to support athletic activities of all kinds. Our Sport Mat, Vulca-NO! Sport, and Next Step ranges are all ideal options for your sporting facility.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8812fab1-7fff-15bf-202c-d1727b33f8e2\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Decks and walkways: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Both decorative and durable, recycled rubber flooring mats are an excellent choice for outdoor locations such as decks, walkways and even roofs. Being an all-weather solution these tiles can be worked into your designs for landscapes, gardens and outside entertainment areas. For decks and walkways, we have created a range of outdoor recycled rubber tiles called NuVista, which provide superior traction and noise reduction for these exterior surfaces.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8812fab1-7fff-15bf-202c-d1727b33f8e2\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Children’s play areas: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber play tiles are water permeable and slip-resistant, providing a comfortable and durable surface on which children can play safely. Check out our Playtiles, a <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">recycled rubber flooring</a> product designed especially for play areas and playgrounds. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8812fab1-7fff-15bf-202c-d1727b33f8e2\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Barns and animal enclosures: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Flooring mats made from recycled, non-vulcanized recycled rubber are tough, odourless and safe for indoor and outdoor use in animal habitats. The dense rubber is easy to clean, provides a non-slip surface for livestock to walk on and facilitates a hygienic environment for animals and the people who care for them. A special addition to our Vulca-NO! range, our Barn Mats create a sure footing for walkways and standing areas for barns, livestock haulers, veterinary clinics, and more.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8812fab1-7fff-15bf-202c-d1727b33f8e2\"><span xss=\"removed\">For more information on all of our <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products\">recycled rubber mat flooring</a> solutions, contact us here at Dinoflex. </span></span></p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-02-09', 1, '2021-02-19 09:32:45', '2021-04-27 06:14:18'),
(13, '20210219094707214.png', 'Dinoflex’s recycled rubber flooring for gyms', 'Dinoflex’s recycled rubber flooring for gyms', 'Dinoflex manufactures rubber flooring for all purposes. Read more about two of our most popular products and their benefits.', 'dinoflex-recycled-rubber-flooring-for-gyms', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-05a78cf2-7fff-efd3-f200-53b625669b2a\"><span xss=\"removed\">Most people looking for <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">recycled rubber</a> flooring have three attributes in mind: aesthetics, durability and sustainability. Those who opt for Dinoflex’s flooring solutions are developing either commercial spaces or sports and fitness facilities. For the former, our Evolution Commercial Flooring is extremely popular as this flooring product brings together design and durability in a recycled rubber flooring mat that can carry the weight of heavy foot traffic, is easy to clean and comes in a range of colours and patterns to suit any visual requirements.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\"><img alt=\"Dinoflex’s recycled rubber flooring for gyms\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/Dinoflex’s recycled rubber flooring for gyms.png\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-985505ca-7fff-16db-3f5a-d7d0fd096826\"><span xss=\"removed\">All-purpose recycled rubber sporting and gym mats</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c9c9da38-7fff-4021-3d25-c8fc8424c678\"><span xss=\"removed\">When it comes to fitness and sporting facilities, our Sport Mat is a popular choice. Incredibly versatile, this <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">gym flooring</a> serves just as effectively in a home gym as it does in a major sporting arena. Sport Mat is our entry-level product, creating a safe workout environment with reduced risk of falls. It can easily take the impact of weights and machines, won’t show any wear patterns, and like all of our products, is guaranteed never to curl. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">With a very low percentage of volatile organic compounds (VOC), a facility’s air quality is not affected by installing this product</span><span xss=\"removed\">. As an additional perk, Sport Mat recycled rubber floor tiles can be branded with your logo, which will not fade over time.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-93ca40b2-7fff-be37-f66d-7bd40262ab9a\"><span xss=\"removed\">Sustainable, designer-friendly recycled rubber floor mats</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-baef88c4-7fff-eb54-e545-ea0c496e23ef\"><span xss=\"removed\">Being made from recycled rubber, all of our products have a high degree of sustainability. Whereas Sport Mat is our entry-level option for flooring, Next Step Extreme is our elite, high-level flooring solution for the serious athlete. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">With radical sound absorption properties, this recycled rubber flooring can safely take all the reps an athlete will give it. Keeping athletes safe is important to us, and Next Step Extreme offers high slip resistance and easy maintenance and cleaning, which is important in a fitness facility. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-9e448d45-7fff-3017-0947-11fdbfff1eb8\"><span xss=\"removed\">Contact Dinoflex to find out more about our <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">gym flooring</a> options and other products.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-02-15', 1, '2021-02-19 09:45:33', '2021-02-24 14:49:26'),
(14, '20210219095441570.png', 'Benefits of designing with recycled rubber flooring ', 'Benefits of designing with recycled rubber flooring ', 'Why is rubber flooring so popular for a variety of applications? Read all about the benefits of recycled rubber flooring.', 'benefits-of-recycled-rubber-floor-tiles', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ef982736-7fff-5e99-f169-b42591e1db31\"><span xss=\"removed\">What makes <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">recycled rubber flooring</a> such a popular choice for so many different applications? It is a versatile and durable material with a variety of functional and aesthetic benefits. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Benefits of designing with recycled rubber flooring \" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/Benefits of designing with recycled rubber flooring.png\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">Let’s take a closer look at the most important benefits of recycled rubber floor tiles:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-7678b7a9-7fff-814f-1b03-5abce23dc76b\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Resilience: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber floors can carry enormous amounts of regular foot traffic, even in high impact conditions. They are also water-resistant and thus impervious to spills and stains, which can easily be washed off. What makes them especially suitable for gyms is that they provide more cushioning than other flooring types, which improves comfort and reduces injuries and fatigue.</span></span></li>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-1b32bcbe-7fff-a8e7-2537-3c73eedf864c\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Slip resistance: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Gyms and similar facilities are places in which injuries are a relatively high risk. Flooring shouldn’t add to these risks. Recycled rubber floors reduce the risk of slipping to an extreme unlikelihood.</span></span></li>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-321f14e3-7fff-d3df-815f-018f296a92ea\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Aesthetic versatility: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber floor mats and tiles can offer a wide range of options to suit your stylistic requirements. They come in almost any colour you like, with a range of patterning and texturing options to complete and accent your designs.</span></span></li>\r\n <li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-86231747-7fff-0299-ba58-0de270ba3a84\"><strong><span xss=\"removed\">Sustainability: </span></strong><span xss=\"removed\">With <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">recycled rubber flooring</a> products such as the Dinoflex range, you can rest assured that you have selected a solution that not only fulfils your stylistic and functional requirements but also reduces the carbon footprint of your facility.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-d686112b-7fff-3792-8d53-d054190586df\"><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber floor mats come in several designs, all of which offer the above-listed benefits with a range of variations to make these products suitable for specific purposes and facilities. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">At Dinoflex, we have a full range of recycled rubber matting options for every purpose, from gyms and sport facilities to commercial spaces and barns. Contact us to find out more about our <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/gym-matting-options-for-commercial-and-home-gyms\">recycled rubber flooring</a> products. </span></span></p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-02-19', 1, '2021-02-19 09:54:41', '2021-02-24 14:50:25');
