(22, NULL, '5 Places that Most Frequently Install Indoor Commercial Flooring', '5 Places that Most Frequently Install Indoor Commercial Flooring', '', '5-Places-that-Most-Frequently-Install-Indoor-Commercial-Flooring', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">Recycled rubber flooring is gaining a reputation for its durability and beauty in commercial applications. Being a highly versatile flooring product that is easily installed, easily maintained and preserves its new-look for a long period of time, recycled rubber flooring offers many benefits. In addition, having your designer and architect incorporate Dinoflex flooring helps your business or commercial property go green with <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products\"> recycled rubber flooring</a>.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<img alt=\"Top 6 uses of rubber mat flooring\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/img-sofa.jpg\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2><strong>5 Most Used Indoor Commercial Flooring Applications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\nDinoflex recycled rubber flooring suits numerous industrial and commercial applications, including:\r\n<ol>\r\n   <li>Hospitals</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n<ol>  \r\n <li>Retail Shops</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n<ol> \r\n <li>Shopping Malls</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n<ol> \r\n <li>Offices</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n<ol> \r\n <li>Fitness Centres</li>\r\n</ol> \r\nFeel free to <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/case_studies\">browse through our case studies</a> to observe how commercial clients are putting our Dinoflex recycled rubber flooring products to use in their building.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Hospitals </h2>\r\n<a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/uploads/case_study/20181016062351696.pdf\"> York Hospital in Pennsylvania </a>replaced disintegrating, unsanitary wood chips in the hospital playground with strong, beautiful recycled rubber tiles. This alternative surface material eliminated expensive annual maintenance and safety issues associated with sharp wood chips. \r\n</p></span>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\nDinoflex recycled rubber flooring also works well in hospital lobbies, waiting rooms, and entrances.\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Retail Shops</h2>\r\nDinoflex indoor commercial recycled rubber flooring comes in a rainbow of colours that retail shops can use to match their branding. Logos, geometric patterns, and bespoke designs provide retail stores with one-of-a-kind flooring that requires little maintenance. The <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/evolution-commercial\"> Dinoflex Evolution series </a> offers the following advantages:\r\n</p></span>\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<ol>\r\n   <li>High traction for customer safety</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n<ol>   \r\n <li>Underfoot comfort that employees and staff members appreciate</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n<ol> \r\n <li>Sound resistance </li>\r\n</ol> \r\n<ol> \r\n <li>Sustainable material for greener buildings</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n</p></span>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Shopping Malls and Museums</h2>\r\nIndividual stores choose their own flooring based on the needs of their business. However, common areas must incorporate attractive materials that can withstand heavy foot traffic that are characteristic of malls and museums. Dinoflex recycled rubber flooring absorbs sound, reducing noise pollution. Additionally, our abrasion-resistant surfaces maintain their original colour and appearance needed in mall walkways, dining areas, and museums. Add to this, the comfort and confidence offered by slip-resistant surfaces inherent in recycled rubber flooring make this choice of flooring ideal for heavily-trafficked establishments.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Offices</h2>\r\nThe <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/uploads/case_study/20181016063616437.pdf\"> Horne Payne Building </a> houses BC Hydro, the major provider of hydroelectric power in British Columbia. The building uses solar panels for hot water and other energy needs. Our recycled rubber flooring was the perfect flooring solution to align with their value on sustainability. BC Hydro incorporated our indoor Evolution commercial flooring in their project and appreciated the easy-maintenance this flooring solution provided.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2> Fitness Centres</h2>\r\nDinoflex recycled rubber flooring is a perfect match for running tracks, weight rooms, and entryways in fitness centres such as CrossFit Vernon and No Limits Fitness. What could durable, attractive, and sustainable rubber flooring do for your commercial fitness centre or gym?\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\"><strong>\r\nFind out more about Dinoflex commercial indoor flooring by calling us at 877-713-1899. You can also fill out our online <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/contact\">contact form</a> and enter the details about your project for a free, no-obligation quote.</strong>\r\n</span>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-06-09', 0, '2021-06-09 03:08:47', '2021-06-09 03:17:33'),
