their value on sustainability. BC Hydro incorporated our indoor Evolution commercial flooring in their project and appreciated the easy-maintenance this flooring solution provided.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2> Fitness Centres</h2>\r\nDinoflex recycled rubber flooring is a perfect match for running tracks, weight rooms, and entryways in fitness centres such as CrossFit Vernon and No Limits Fitness. What could durable, attractive, and sustainable rubber flooring do for your commercial fitness centre or gym?\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\"><strong>\r\nFind out more about Dinoflex commercial indoor flooring by calling us at 877-713-1899. You can also fill out our online <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/contact\">contact form</a> and enter the details about your project for a free, no-obligation quote.</strong>\r\n</span>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-06-09', 1, '2021-06-09 03:09:14', '2021-06-09 03:21:02'),
(24, '20210609032257356.jpg', 'Why Commercial Areas Must Have Easy-to-Clean Floors', 'Why Commercial Areas Must Have Easy-to-Clean Floors', '', 'Why-Commercial-Areas-Must-Have-Easy-to-Clean-Floors', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\nCommercial areas face heavy foot traffic and present potential liability risk if someone slips and falls. You can reduce accidents with recycled rubber floors that provide comfort and traction underfoot, provide slip-resistant surfaces and are easy-to-clean, keeping your customers and employees safe. Read below to understand how recycled rubber flooring fits into your commercial building maintenance strategy, especially since all Dinoflex products come with <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/uploads/product_resources_documents/2020061305181374.pdf\"> detailed cleaning instructions </a> to help you keep your recycled rubber flooring looking like new for years to come.</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<img alt=\"Top 6 uses of rubber mat flooring\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/20210609post2.jpg\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Recycled Rubber Flooring Is Low-Maintenance </h2> \r\nRain, snow, and other inclement weather conditions can cause a sloshy mess in your lobby and hallways. Students, shoppers, and guests can spill food, water, soda, and other beverages as they move through public areas in your commercial building. However, you can use recycled rubber flooring to reduce slip and fall accidents due to wet floors. \r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\nHealth inspectors, employees, guests, and customers all judge a business by the appearance and cleanliness of its premises. With recycled rubber flooring, your guests will happily put their best foot forward on easy to maintain rubber tiles. </span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\nThanks to the global pandemic, everyone remains on hyper alert status when it comes to sanitation and safety. With recycled rubber floors in your building, you can clean up spills and stains in moments to maintain the original aesthetic of your flooring. </span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/\"> Choose from Dinoflex products</a> designed for your industrial or commercial applications to match the colour, style, and durability your organization depends on to prevent accidents and keep customers coming back.</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>How Do You Clean Anti-Slip Recycled Rubber Flooring?</h2>\r\nClean our Dinoflex recycled rubber flooring in three easy steps:\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Sweep the floor with a broom to remove dirt and debris. If you use a vacuum cleaner, choose one without bristles because they can scratch the floor. Using a vacuum with high suction power removes more dirt and debris and makes mopping easier. </li>\r\n<li>Spot-clean the floor. Give set-in stains extra attention by scrubbing them with a soft brush.</li>\r\n<li>Mop the floor. We recommend using a nylon, sponge, or microfibre mop to avoid soaking the rubber flooring. Take care not to leave puddles by the seams where moisture can find its way to your subflooring.</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n<p>\r\nUse a microfibre, sponge, or nylon mop to soak up puddles and spills between cleanings. </p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h3>  DinoClean  Safely Cleans Your Rubber Floors</h3>\r\n<a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/dino-clean\">DinoClean </a> is an eco-friendly product specifically designed for recycled rubber flooring. It’s neutral PH cleansing ingredients also clean and shine other types of hard flooring materials. DinoClean has low-foaming properties, so you can use it in mopping buckets and auto scrubbers to remove dirt and leave behind a crisp, clean scent. \r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<strong>\r\nReduce slip and fall accidents and maintain your Dinoflex recycled rubber floors by following the steps above. You can call us at 877-713-1899 for more information on our commercial flooring and rubber floor maintenance products. Take a few minutes to fill out our  <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/contact\"> contact form </a>, if you would like more information for your project. </strong> \r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<p><strong>Reference:</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.flooringinc.com/blog/how-to-clean-rubber-gym-flooring/\"> How to Clean Rubber Gym Flooring: 4 Easy Steps - Flooring Inc </a></p>\r\n</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-06-09', 1, '2021-06-09 03:22:57', '2021-06-09 03:57:17'),
(25, '20210609032447941.jpg', 'Customize Flooring Space with Dinoflex Solutions', 'Customize Flooring Space with Dinoflex Solutions', '', 'Customize-Flooring-Space-with-Dinoflex-Solutions', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\nWith a range of colour and shape options, Dinoflex recycled rubber floors customize flooring space for industrial, commercial, educational, and other specializations. Architects, contractors, and interior designers are now recommending this flexible, renewable construction material to every type of organization. \r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<img alt=\"Top 6 uses of rubber mat flooring\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/20210609post3.jpg\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Any Pattern or Shape</h2>\r\nUsing EPDM mats made of coarse and fine granules, here at Dinoflex we manufacture  precisely-cut recycled rubber flooring into complex shapes, including the following:\r\n<ol>\r\n <li>Geometric shapes to add interest in rooms or public areas</li>\r\n <li>School mascots and team colors in patterns of your choice</li>\r\n <li>Customized tiles for areas where you want to make an impression</li>\r\n</ol> \r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h3>Colour Innovation</h3>\r\nAt Dinoflex, we offer over 26 colours but you can further customize your floor colour in our <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/color-innovator/\"> Colour Innovator </a> studio. If you’re stuck for ideas, contact us directly and we’ll help you find inspiration in a bouquet of flowers or colours and patterns inspired by nature. Our precise colour matching tools make it easy to design a custom, beautiful layout for your commercial flooring. \r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Use on Stairs</h2>\r\nThe stairwell in your school, commercial building, industrial complex, or office building probably receives more foot traffic than any other area of your building. When wet, stairs can become dirty and slippery, leaving a poor impression, and potentially causing accidents.\r\nWhen you install recycled rubber flooring on your stairs, you can prevent slip and fall accidents and make it easier for occupants to maneuver up and down stairwells without incident. Rubber flooring in general also makes it easier to clean and maintain stairwells and provides traction for those travelling between floors.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\nIf you would like advice or assistance on using Dinoflex recycled rubber flooring on commercial stairwells, contact us anytime.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Match Your Corporate Image</h2>\r\nWhether you own a retail shop, shopping center, or large manufacturing plant, at Dinoflex, we can create <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/custom-floor-design-and-logos\"> custom floor designs and logos </a> to match your corporate image. Customize flooring space in your office building with our recycled rubber flooring. As a leading <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/about-us\"> commercial flooring provider </a>, we have pushed the limits on technology to meet the demands of our corporate and retails consumers. We work with architects and designers to create logos, patterns, and vivid colours that customers, vendors, employees, and potential investors will notice. \r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<strong> \r\nTo customize flooring space, stairs, and lobbies with sustainable recycled rubber flooring, call Dinoflex at 877-713-1899. Fill out our <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/contact\"> contact form </a> to discuss any pattern or colours you may have in mind.\r\n</strong>\r\n</span></p> \r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-06-09', 1, '2021-06-09 03:24:47', NULL),
(26, '20210609032634751.jpg', 'Indoor Commercial Flooring Q&A', 'Indoor Commercial Flooring Q&A', '', 'Indoor-Commercial-Flooring-QA', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\nDinoflex recycled rubber floors are suitable for high traffic areas in your commercial building. Whether you need durable, attractive flooring for an office building, industrial space, school, or shopping mall, we have customized products for a variety of uses. Keep reading for answers to our most frequently asked questions.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<img alt=\"Top 6 uses of rubber mat flooring\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/admin_upload/images/20210609post4.jpg\" xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>How Durable and Resilient Is Recycled Rubber Flooring?</h2>\r\nRecycled rubber floors withstand heavy-duty use in high traffic areas. Rubber has a natural elasticity that makes it the perfect material for commercial flooring. Dinoflex recycled rubber flooring absorbs impacts and cleans up easily to help you keep it looking like new for many years. It also absorbs sound to help keep down the noise in hallways, wait rooms and other loud areas that can transfer noise to other rooms and floors.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Is Recycled Rubber Flooring Waterproof?</h2>\r\nYes! Rubber flooring doesn\'t absorb spilled beverages, melted snow or rain, or mop water, making it easy to maintain and clean up. Sealing the seams between tiles that lay tightly together or interlock can make your recycled rubber flooring even more water resistant. \r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>How Expensive Is Recycled Rubber Flooring?</h2>\r\nThe price range of our high-quality, strong, and resilient rubber flooring is very competitive. For a free quote, <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/contact\"> fill out our customer contact form </a> with details about your commercial flooring project. One of our representatives will get back to you quickly with a free quote and advise on how to make your project more cost-effective.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>Is Recycled Rubber Flooring Environmentally Friendly?</h2>\r\nVery! Dinoflex rubber flooring is made from recycled commercial truck tires that have been taken out of the landfill. Additionally, our recycled rubber flooring can be further recycled at the end of its useful life. Low VOC, renewable rubber flooring can help you create a greener building without sacrificing indoor air quality.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<h2>What Type of Recycled Rubber Flooring Should I Use?</h2></span>\r\n<p>\r\nCommercial recycled rubber flooring makes a great base for your high traffic areas. Add style to your fitness room, retail space, office building, and other commercial applications and <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/case_studies\"> review our case studies </a> for ideas on where and how to use our commercial recycled rubber flooring. \r\n Our <a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/products/custom-floor-design-and-logos\">products page  </a> also provides great insight to match your facility with the right Dinoflex recycled rubber flooring. </p>\r\n<p>Choose the right flooring option for these commercial and public spaces:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li>Commercial/Retail</li>\r\n <li>Hospitality</li>\r\n <li>Ice Arena</li>\r\n <li>Fitness/Sport</li>\r\n <li>Health Care</li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://dinoflex.com/best-use/education\"> Education</a></li>\r\n</ol> \r\n\r\n</p>\r\n</span> \r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n <strong>\r\nCall Dinoflex at 877-713-1899 for assistance with any questions you have on how to use our sustainable, beautiful rubber flooring in your high traffic areas. </strong>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n<p><strong>References</strong></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.rubberflooringinc.com/buyers-guide/rubber-flooring-faq.html\"> https://www.rubberflooringinc.com/buyers-guide/rubber-flooring-faq.html</a>\r\n</span></p>', 'Dinoflex Recycled Rubber Flooring', '2021-06-09', 1, '2021-06-09 03:26:09', '2021-06-09 03:54:04');
INSERT INTO `case_study` (`id`, `banner_image`, `header_title`, `browsertitle`, `header_content`, `section_title1`, `section_title2`, `section_content`, `status`, `created_datetime`, `modified_datetime`) VALUES
(1, '20190826181846437.jpg', 'Case Studies', 'Case Studies', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; color:#fff;\">Over the years Dinoflex has provided a diverse solutions to architects, designers, and business partners. Here are just a few of their projects and the success they found with Dinoflex.</p>\r\n', 'Case Studies', 'Testimonials', 'It&#39;s a great product - durable, sustainable, easy to maintain and attractive. The installation in my office has become a great way of convincing my clients to use the products. If they are initially put off by the idea of rubber flooring made from recycled tires, see how great it looks quickly changes their minds.<span class=\"quotes_end position-relative\" style=\"line-height: 0.8em;float: none; vertical-align: text-top;\">&quot;</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"yellow-txt\"><b>Kevin Hanvey, MAIBC,</b> <small>Principal &amp; Director of sustainability, Omicron Architecture</small></p>\r\n', 1, '2018-10-03 04:44:20', '2020-02-07 20:19:11');
