(21, 'Hans Cummings', 'Ag Mats', 'hcummings@nrha.org', '3173703469', 'My name is Hans Cummings and I am a production editor for Hardware Retailing magazine. I would like to personally congratulate you for having Ag Mats selected by our Retailers\' Choice Committee as one of the most innovative items featured at the recent National Hardware Virtual Show.\r\n\r\nYou should be very proud of this honor. Unlike many other product awards, we do not have an editorial panel select our winners. Your product was selected by a panel of retailers who have real-world experience in identifying unique merchandise that holds the potential for retail sales.\r\n\r\nHere are a few more facts about the awards:\r\n\r\n•   Hardware Retailing has been handing out the Retailers’ Choice Awards at the National Hardware Show® for more than 50 years.\r\n\r\n•   Each of the winners is selected from the thousands of products on display at the show.\r\n\r\n•   This year there were 31 products selected for these awards.\r\n\r\n•   Judges were asked to explore the virtual show in search of products they found unique and that would do well in their businesses.\r\n\r\nAs a winner, your product will be featured in a special Retailers’ Choice section in the January 2021 issue of Hardware Retailing magazine and it will be promoted in a product video. Additionally, you will receive a plaque recognizing your accomplishment.\r\n\r\n **To be featured in the January issue of Hardware Retailing, I will need you to send me a high-res image of your product (at least 300 DPI) and a paragraph (between 50 and 75 words) stating your product’s features. To have your product included in our product video, please send it to Attn: Dan Tratensek, 136 N. Delaware St., Suite 200, Indianapolis, IN 46204. Also, I will need the correct spelling of the product’s name, company name and mailing address to be featured on the plaque by December 4.**\r\n\r\nOnce you respond, I can provide Retailers’ Choice logos in color and black and white formats. Please feel free to use the logo on any packaging, website or promotions for your product and company. \r\n\r\n Please don\'t hesitate to contact me if you have any questions.\r\n\r\nThank you for your help, and again, congratulations on your Retailers’ Choice Award win!\r\n', '2020-12-01'),
