(225, 'Gene Carr', 'Online Reputation', 'GeneCarr0410@gmail.com', '', 'Hello, \r\n\r\nDo your online reviews give your customers confidence to buy from you?  Customers are very savvy these days and will cyber-stalk you before buying.  Your reviews need to be good in order for them to buy.  If you don\'t have enough good reviews, they will not trust you and buy from someone who does.  If you have bad reviews, they will go with someone that has good ones.  Most companies don\'t even realize the massive amount of sales they\'re missing out on by having bad reviews or not enough reviews.  \r\n\r\nWe have helped many companies to improve their reputation online, by pushing negative reviews down in the search engines and reviews sites, and by getting many reviews removed completely.  We have a variety of tricks up our sleeve to clear up your reputation, and even more tricks to get you good reviews on an ongoing basis while suppressing negative reviews.  \r\n\r\nI would like to tell you more about our services and how they can help you.  Do you have time in the next few days for a consultation on what we can do for you, what the costs are, how long it will take, and what our services have done for our other clients?  We\'d love to share the information with you and think it will help you whether you decide to use our services or not (there\'s no pressure).  \r\n\r\nPlease just let me know if you\'d like more info and we can setup a time to chat.  \r\n\r\nMany thanks!\n\nThanks.\r\nGene Carr', '2021-05-14'),
