(7, 'Nature’s Collection Cork Infused Flooring - Naturally Elegant. Naturally Beautiful.', 'natures-collection', 1, NULL, '20190613063520539.png', '20200626182606160.jpg', 'Nature’s Collection Cork Infused Flooring - ', 'Naturally Elegant. Naturally Beautiful.', 'Nature’s Collection Cork Infused Flooring - Naturally Elegant. Naturally Beautiful.', 'Sophisticated and elegant, Nature&rsquo;s Collection blends the durability and versatility of recycled rubber with the style of sustainably harvested cork. By infusing cork granules we add depth and texture to the surface, while the vivid colors of the EPDM offer contrast, coming together for a perfectly balanced design that is sure to leave you impressed.', 'Sophisticated and elegant, Nature&rsquo;s Collection blends the warmth and comfort of recycled rubber with the style and sustainably of harvested cork.', 'Made for Designers ', 'We have combined characteristics that are similar yet complimentary to one another giving you a product with superb performance and a visual dimension not typically found with rubber surfaces.', '105,28,107,2,106,108,12,104', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Renewable source which does not harm the planet</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Design a space that is uniquely different</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Spaces will hold heat and remain warm</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Resists abrasions and indentations, resulting in a long-life expectancy</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Provides relief to a person who stands for long periods of time</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Great for high moisture environment areas</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Increased acoustic properties over other resilient products</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Eliminates the need for non-slip&nbsp;matting</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '11,10,35,36,34,12', '<div class=\"col-md-5\"><img alt=\"Interlock Tile\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/frontside/images/interlocking_floor.png\" /><strong>Interlocking Floor (Loose Lay)</strong><br />\r\n<br 