(8, 'NEXT STEP™ High Impact - Keep athletes in the game.', 'high-impact', 1, 'Shock-absorbing flooring tiles for Gyms and Sports Facilities. Interlocking rubber for Athletic Flooring that absorbs impact and reduces sound', '20190613063640886.png', '20200626193030350.jpg', 'Athletic Flooring -', ' Next Step High Impact', 'Athletic Flooring | NEXT STEP High Impact | Athletic Gym Floor', '<br>\r\nNEXT STEP™ High Impact works hard so athletes can play hard. The highly durable backing gives support for prolonged training endurance while our NEXT STEP™ wear layer allows you to showcase your team colors with pride. With a surface this good; all the athlete needs to do is focus on is their training.', 'Welcome every type of athlete with confidence; there is nothing Next Step High Impact can&rsquo;t handle.', 'Shock Absorbing. Slip Resistant.', 'Welcome every type of athlete with confidence, knowing there&rsquo;s nothing NEXT STEP&trade; High Impact can&rsquo;t handle. Provide stability with our high-traction surfacing, ensuring athletes don&rsquo;t get injured when lifting. It&rsquo;s perfect for all facilities.', '45,115,114,112,111,25,24,113', '', '<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n <p>Can withstand abuse from heavy weights</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p>Provides grip, reducing risk of injury</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p>Deadens sound caused by weights dropping</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p>Force is sent back into the weight, protecting your subfloor</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p>Materials are made from manufacturing waste, saving costs and the environment</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p>Remove sweat, dirt and grime with ease, keeping your floor fresh</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p>Prevents unsightly stains that can affect how your environment is viewed</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n <p>High Impact backing can be applied to any Dinoflex color</p>\r\n </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '44,48,83,84', '<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<p><img alt=\"Interlock Tile\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/frontside/images/interlo