(11, 'NuVista® Tiles - Durable Enough for the Toughest Climates', 'nuvista-tiles', 2, NULL, '20190613064326382.png', '20200831210317973.jpg', 'NuVista® Tiles - ', 'Outdoor living at its most beautiful.', 'NuVista® Tiles - Durable Enough for the Toughest Climates', '<br />\r\nDinoflex NuVista&reg; Tiles provide a durable, high traction decorative landscape surface for rooftop areas and ground level locations when you are looking to revitalize the space. Suitable for rooftop patio retreats and community gardens, landscape designs and sophisticated green roof systems resilient rubber paver tiles are an all-weather solution for year-round use.', 'NuVista&reg; Tiles&nbsp;provide superior noise reduction and high traction surfacing for rooftop patios, decks or walkways for many applications.', 'Durable Enough for the Toughest Climates', 'Proven performance in the harshest climatic conditions, these impact and sound reducing tiles provide superior protection for rooftop membranes.', '30,128,110,39,120,127', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Slip resistant even when wet</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Will not buckle or crack in temperature changes</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Reduces fall consequences</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Creates channels for water drainage</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Easy and quick installation</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Advanced maintenance program not required</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2,89,90,6,88,3,86,5,1,4,68', '<div class=\"col-md-6\"><img alt=\"Interlock Tile\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/frontside/images/interlocking_tile_grey_stride.png\" /><strong>Interlocking Tile</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Size</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>24&rdquo; x 24&rdquo; = 4ft&sup2; (61cm x 61cm = 0.37m&sup2;)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<p><strong>Standard Thickness</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1&rdquo; (25.4mm), 1 3/4&rdquo;&nbsp;(44mm), 2 1/2&rdquo; (64mm)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 15, '2018-10-1