(12, 'PlayTiles® - Let Kids be Kids', 'playground-tiles', 2, NULL, '20190613064358183.png', '20200831210052335.jpg', 'PlayTiles® - ', 'Let Kids be Kids', 'PlayTiles® - Let Kids be Kids', '<br />\r\nDinoflex PlayTiles&reg; create a safe place to let kids be kids. Parents will have peace of mind knowing their kids are playing on an ASTM certified surface. Specially designed to reduce injuries from falls, kids can run, jump, swing, and slide on a product that supports play.', 'Specifically designed to reduce injuries from falls, Dinoflex PlayTiles&reg; create a safe place to let kids be kids, so let them play!', 'Water Permeable and Slip Resistant', 'Tough enough to stand up to any weather condition and the most active children, PlayTiles allow your kids to play on a dry surface after a rain storm and get them back outside quickly.', '84,130,53,2,131,129,50', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Reduces injuries from falls</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Slip resistant even when wet</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Solid surface provides a visible environment for impurities and hazards</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Easily installs on compacted soft ground or solid surfaces</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Tiles can be installed in any season</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Withstands any wear and tear</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Creates an inclusive play space for all</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '42,33,39,41,54,4', '<div class=\"col-md-6\"><img alt=\"Interlock Tile\" src=\"https://dinoflex.com/frontside/images/interlocking_tile_grey_stride.png\" /><strong>Interlocking Tile</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Size</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>24&rdquo; x 24&rdquo; = 4ft&sup2; (61cm x 61cm = 0.37m&sup2;)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<p><strong>Thickness</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1 1/2&rdquo; (38mm)</li>\r\n	<li>2 1/4&rdquo; (57mm)</li>\r\n	<li>3 1/2&rdquo; (89mm)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<p><str