(1, 'Create your custom tile', '<ol>\r\n\r\n<li>Choose your application</li>\r\n\r\n</ol>', 'COLOR ROOM', '<ul>\r\n									<li>Please select your base colors</li>\r\n									<li>Choose up to 5 colors (Black is automatically selected)</li>\r\n									<li>All colors with a COARSE / FINE option may be selected twice.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'INNOVATION STATION', '<ul>\r\n									<li>Play with the percentages of your selected colors.</li>\r\n									<li>Toggle between COARSE and FINE options for a different look.</li>\r\n									<li>All swatches require a minimum of 15% FINE option.</li>\r\n																	<li>Black is preset to the minimum of 5%  however you can increase it.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Percentages can be comprised of a maximum of 5 colors plus Black.</li>\r\n<li>If you are creating swatches for \"STRIDE FITNESS TILES\", make sure that Black is set to a minimum of 20%.\r\n</li>								</ul>', 'INNOVATION STATION', '<ul> 									<li>Play with the percentages of your selected colors.</li> 									<li>Toggle between the COARSE and FINE options for a different look.</li> 									<li>Black is preset to the minimum of 20%  however you can increase it.</li> 																	<li>Percentages can be comprised of a maximum of 5 colors plus Black.</li> 								</ul>', 'YOUR CUSTOM SWATCH', '<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>&nbsp;You can request a sample of any swatch you create.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Every swatch can be sent as an email should you need to send it to others, or simply just want to keep it for yourself. </strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>If you&rsquo;d like to keep your swatch tile creations, please register an account. Please note: only one Gallery can be created per email address.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>If you choose not to register an account, your swatch creations will be erased when you leave the Color Conductor.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 'PLACE', '<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>You can place your creations into sample room scenes.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>You can send copies of your creations along with your creation in different environments to yourself via email.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '2018-06-01 17:06:55', '2019-01-09 22:18:13');
